00:29:00.280 --> 00:29:03.500
And he ws generous with
all of it, you know.

00:29:03.500 --> 00:29:09.730
And so I thanked him and I still
have those and display those.

00:29:09.730 --> 00:29:16.700
Well, here is my longest
second trip in beginning.

00:29:16.700 --> 00:29:18.910
This is 1993.

