00:36:48.190 --> 00:36:51.940
you know, she's just a
beautiful woman in spirit

00:36:51.940 --> 00:36:56.450
and telling this story and
at the same time being able

00:36:56.450 --> 00:36:58.210
to smile for the photograph.

00:36:58.210 --> 00:37:02.470
And, she's proud that,
you know, that she had it

00:37:02.470 --> 00:37:07.800
and that there was the interest
in for it to be restored.

00:37:07.800 --> 00:37:10.300
When I heard that, that
