00:37:10.300 --> 00:37:15.280
So I, so everything
starts to evolve.

00:37:15.280 --> 00:37:22.510
And then, some of them
take on different stories.

00:37:22.510 --> 00:37:29.550
And, we show you this one
because Wade Maynard turned 100.

00:37:29.550 --> 00:37:30.850
Correct?

00:37:30.850 --> 00:37:32.150
&gt;&gt; Barry Bergey: Right.

00:37:32.150 --> 00:37:36.500
&gt;&gt; Tom Pich: So, Barry and I
that day, that day met and,

00:37:36.500 --> 00:37:40.710
in Michigan and drove
up to their house to,

00:37:40.710 --> 00:37:43.340
Barry was presenting
him with a plaque or.

00:37:43.340 --> 00:37:46.210
&gt;&gt; Barry Bergey: We were giving
him a letter from the Chairman

00:37:46.210 --> 00:37:48.960
of the National Endowment for
